{"about_the_game":"Becastled is about building and defending your castle from sieges in a fantasy world!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330460/extras/siege_tower.gif?t=1737730255\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330460/extras/enemy_horde.gif?t=1737730255\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Build your castle</strong>. Find a good place to place your keep and build defenses around it. You can place walls, gates and towers. Position your archers on them to shoot enemies at night.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330460/extras/wood_production.gif?t=1737730255\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Gather resources</strong>. You will have to manage the economy of your city. Gather resources to build new buildings and to maintain your workers and army.<br><br></li><li><strong>Train an army</strong>. Train your troops so that you will be ready to meet the enemy at night. You can also upgrade your troops with a new shining armor in the armory.<br><br></li><li><strong>Expand your city</strong>. Capture more territories to get access to new resources. Build more houses to have a place for new people. More workers will be able to create a better economy and sustain a bigger army. There are some production chains. All of that will making you busy during the day<br><br></li><li><strong>Siege engines</strong>. Trebuchets and ballistas can help to protect your castle. You can place them on top of towers. Make sure you have enough ammo for them to shoot.<br><br></li><li><strong>Survive a siege</strong>. Each night you are being attacked by moon monsters, the more your play the more powerful is their attack. How long can you survive? Enemies can have rams or siege towers to break through walls.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse